description: A measure of the utilized computation power relative to the total allowance of the CU. Range from 0 to 1.
A measure of the used capacity relative to the total capacity of the CU. Range from 0 to 1.
The current amount of persistent storage consumed by data and indexes.
A measure of current write operations relative to the total write rate limit. Range from 0 to 1.
The total number of slow requests.
Total number of vectors across requests, e.g., total number of ingested vectors across insert requests, or total number of target input vectors across search requests.
The average latency of requests processed.
The 99 percentile latency of requests processed.
The current number of loaded entities.
The current number of unloaded collections.
